Template-Pluginâ€”Date-FriendlyDelta version 0.01
==========================================

Template::Plugin::Date::FriendlyDelta is a Template Toolkit Filter Plugin for showing the date delta for a supplied date and now in human-readable form.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  DateTime
  Date::Parse

